reviewText: Met him when we were both in the service we shot together in Germany he is a good instructor
Good solid advice from someone who knows something and knows how to tell you what he is trying to say
Great training  video follow the instruction and watch your scores improve.

Can't argue with a competitor as accomplished as Dan Carlisle. I'm not sure the third angle of the right triangle really has significance in determining lead though. It is a good pneumonic device, however.
